You need to use [Nested Mapping](https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/nested.html).

Nested type is different from object types, you will get difference in above link.

Query_String doesn&#39;t work on nested types, from the [docs](https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/query-dsl-query-string-query.html#query-string-nested)

&gt; Avoid using the query_string query for nested documentsedit
&gt; query_string searches do not return nested documents. To search nested
&gt; documents, use the nested query.

Mapping:
````
PUT nestedindex
{
  &quot;mappings&quot;: {
    &quot;properties&quot;: {
     &quot;Product&quot;:{
       &quot;type&quot;:&quot;nested&quot;,
       &quot;properties&quot;: {
         &quot;Name&quot;:{
           &quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,
           &quot;fields&quot;:{
             &quot;keyword&quot;:{
               &quot;type&quot;:&quot;keyword&quot;
             }
           }
         },
         &quot;Version&quot;:{
           &quot;type&quot;:&quot;integer&quot;
         }
       }
     } 
    }
  }
}
````
Query:
